    "monster3563": "<h1 class=monster>Hobgoblin Zombie<br><span class=type>Medium natural animate (undead)</span><br><span class=level>Level 2 Brute<span class=xp> XP 125</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> -1        <b>Senses</b> Perception +0; Darkvision<br><b>HP</b> 40; <b>Bloodied</b> 20<br><b>AC</b> 15; <b>Fortitude</b> 15, <b>Reflex</b> 11, <b>Will</b> 12<br><b>Immune</b> disease, poison; <b>Resist</b> 10 necrotic; <b>Vulnerable</b> 5 radiant<br><b>Speed</b> 4</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Slam</b> (standard, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>+6 vs AC; 2d6 + 2 damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Zombie Grab</b> (standard; requires a free hand, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>+4 vs Reflex; the target is grabbed. Checks made to escape the hobgoblin zombie's grab take a -5 penalty. </p><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Zombie Weakness</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>A critical hit to a hobgoblin zombie reduces it to 0 hit points instantly.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Unaligned       <b> Languages</b> -<br><b>Str</b> 17 (+4)      <b>Dex</b> 6 (-1)      <b>Wis</b> 8 (0)<br><b>Con</b> 10 (+1)      <b>Int</b> 1 (-4)      <b>Cha</b> 3 (-3)</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in Seekers of the Ashen Crown, page(s) 49, Dungeon Magazine 176, page(s) 35.</p>",
